   Bugs fixed in this release
   **************************

   Bug # 246774 - Layer transition info not being kept
   Bug # 301070 - OK and Cancel need to be switched about
   Bug # 301072 - Option to scale project to screenshot size
   Bug # 315731 - Crash/image distortion on changing the zoom level
   Bug # 361019 - no icons for all windows of salasaga
   Bug # 480491 - Some characters not being displayed correctly in the working area
   Bug # 492388 - Cannot edit new text
   Bug # 493312 - Cannot use keyboard to delete layer


